{"tid":684913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 乃木坂46主將齋藤飛鳥 下海與男優拍AV版 [那些年] ??","createTime":"2018-05-31T03:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T10:52:57.000Z","uid":133529,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ab94f81be1c8f3ba1b268804eb8191759276e753","tid":684913,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T03:33:08.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】改編自台灣作家九把刀同名小說的電影《那些年，我們一起追的女孩》，2011年在港上映，票房勁收6185萬港元，一度成為香港史上最賣座的華語片。早前有日本電影公司購下版權，請來女團乃木坂46主將齋藤飛鳥扮演日版沈佳宜，從昨日發放首條預告片可見，無論造型與氣質都忠於原著，甚至有台灣網民覺得她比陳妍希更像沈佳宜。<br />\n<br />\n《那些年》講述柯震東飾演頑皮中學生柯景騰，愛上陳妍希扮演品學兼優女同學沈佳宜的青春校園故事，2011年上映票房累收4.25億台幣（約1.1億港元），更贏得台灣金馬獎及香港金像獎等多個獎項，早前有日本電影公司購下版權重拍，並將於10月上映，令亞洲影迷相當期待。<br />\n<br />\n《山本五十六》導演操刀<br />\n<br />\n日版《那些年》由《山本五十六》導演長谷川康夫執導，電影《亞人》男星山田裕貴和女團乃木坂46成員齋藤飛鳥合演。原裝版本故事設定在1994年的台灣彰化縣，日版則押後至2000年代的日本為背景。不過，從昨日電影公司首次發放30秒預告片段可見，大部分畫面都熟口熟面，幾乎把台版《那些年》經典場面搬字過紙。<br />\n<br />\n經典場面跟到十足<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180531/s00016/1527703905325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180531%2Fs00016%2F1527703905325&d=7Lzt2Sd01zZBx4VPuSgMEZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a56fc2e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180531%2Fs00016%2F1527703905325&h=9841a2b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180531/s00016/1527703905325</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">乃木坂46主將齋藤飛鳥</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/01/16/1217237-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F1217237-XXL.jpg&h=5be42a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1990000/1990740/20180115_year_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1990000%2F1990740%2F20180115_year_01_1024.jpg&h=5017710c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">飛鳥 與戲中AV男優合照</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171026/photo/bkn-20171026130017289-1026_00862_001_01p.jpg?20171026145925\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171026%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171026130017289-1026_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20171026145925&h=56a4dc8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">AV男優: ムータン</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://img.recordchina.co.jp/thumbs/m720/201710/20171027-044114018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimg.recordchina.co.jp%2Fthumbs%2Fm720%2F201710%2F20171027-044114018.jpg&h=6fa98ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上位男星:山田裕貴</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://blog-imgs-31.fc2.com/n/o/n/nonkeav/moominprgazou1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-31.fc2.com%2Fn%2Fo%2Fn%2Fnonkeav%2Fmoominprgazou1.jpg&h=92120cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/peachjoy/imgs/8/4/84460d56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fpeachjoy%2Fimgs%2F8%2F4%2F84460d56.jpg&h=faea6bd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"